sub_title: Sr. Solution Delivery Manager EMEA at OutSystems
summary:
I have passion for digitalization and innovation. I am driven to tackle challenges, motivate people and provide objective guidance and encouragement for their activities. 

I began my professional career working as a sustainability consultant at a startup company of VolkerWessels. I gained experience in the field of Innovation and IT as business consultant for Atos Consulting and as management consultant in the Digital Advisory group of KPMG Management Consulting both in the Netherlands and Singapore, Currently, I am working for OutSystems, the number one low-code platform.  I am responsible for identifying and setting up large digital transformation programs.
